Now with level 65 being the limit, how many people does it take to kill him? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aauminki>Aauminki</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 1272<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/02 11:56 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> We did him pre-PoP with 42, I'm sure guilds überer than us have done him with less. Haven't killed him after PoP came out. <p><big><center><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=19405 target=blank>Marshall Sscaley Iceblade</a><br><i><a href=http://companions.windsofstorm.net>The Companions ~ Team Headstart</a></i> <br>
Overlizard on Tribunal</big><br><small>"Tails are not for biting or pulling!"</small></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rani>rani</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 103<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/02 12:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> We usually did him with 50 or so pre-PoP. Havent been back since. <br>
<br>
But the 4th and 5th guild on our server are now killing him regularly, so he must be pretty easy by now with level 65 tanks. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fatzthetroll>Fatz the troll</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/02 2:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> My question on AoW is, with a raid force of about 42-48ish people, 3 tanks all of whom have approx. 7300-7400hp raid buffed, one of which has 8300ish hp and is lvl 65, how many clerics would we need to keep the cycle up long enough to kill AoW? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rani>rani</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/02 2:58 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> IMO take your raid there and practice on Idol without slowing it. If you can successfully kill idol unslowed, you should have a decent shot at AoW. <br>
<br>
If you cant, just take the wipe, and make adjustments until you can. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
But for a first try I would take something like minimum 6, preferably 8 clerics. Wether or not they run out of mana before you can kill him depend alot on your DPS I guess.<br>
<br>
A level 65 8300 hp MT should have a good chance of making it through the entire fight, if the CH chain is working correctly and if he have the appropriate defensive aa's. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=warlordcrystara>WarlordCrystara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/02 4:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> I have single tanked our last 3 AoW fights, I have about 8500hp buffed, and it has yet to be a problem not switching, about 8 clerics seems to do the trick. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=141022"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.houston.rr.com/apoctyliptic/pictures/boards/crystara/Crystara65.jpg " style="height:250;width:248;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
&quot;Yea, though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I shall fear no evil.<br>
For I am the meanist son of a bitch in the valley.&quot; <br>
- Marshall Crystara</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bumbleroot>Bumbleroot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/2/02 12:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> I appreciate the information. It appears that it takes about 50 people at level 60 to kill him.<br>
I'm not really looking for a comparison  on the statue to the avatar, what I'm looking for is a number of people that it would take to kill him at level 65. The reason I'm looking for this is to figure out what size of a guild to grow to or what size of a raiding party to have to kill him. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xenojones>XENOJONES</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 511<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/3/02 12:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> 54 with 7 clerics right after POP came out and 45  with 5 clerics three weeks after POP was out. <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Rollen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dumeshuhlbelk>Dumesh UhlBelk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 365<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/3/02 1:37 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://bellsouthpwp.net/w/i/wilsonua/Stare.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Avatar of War</span><hr size=1> My guild kills him regularly with a force from 38-44, about 8-14 are level 65, the rest are all over the map from level 59-64.  The two MTs are 65, and we have 6-7 clerics in rotation, and 1-2 out of rotation (two with the worst connections) who throw in heals when they can.  Our two big tanks are in the low 8000s hp wise.<br>
<br>
Been said many times, but since the spawn is blowwable, it is worth saying again.  Test yourself on the idol, unslowed.  It your run is smooth, then go for it. Good Luck. <p><a href = "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5309"target="_blank"alt = "Korak's Megalo Profile"><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR = 10,10,900><b>Korak Sarathai - Barbarian Warlord - The Hand</b></FONT><BR></a><a href = "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12530"target="_blank"alt = "Dumesh's Megalo Profile"><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR = 900,10,10><b>Dumesh Uhl'Belk - Retired Troll Reaver - The Hand</b></FONT><BR></a>This is my sword. There are many like it, but this one is mine. My sword is my best friend. It is my life. I must master it, as I must master my life. Without me, my sword is useless. Without my sword, I am useless. I must swing my sword true. I must strike deeper than my enemy, who is trying to kill me. I must slay him before he slays me. I will. Before The Tribunal, I swear this creed: my sword and myself are defenders of my land, we are the masters of my enemy, we are the saviors of my life. So be it, until there is no enemy, but peace.</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showPrevMessage?topicID=1552.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showNextMessage?topicID=1552.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.emailToFriend?topicID=1552.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.threadControl?topicID=1552.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteTh